## Third-Party Data & Assets

### Pokémon Data
This application uses data from PokéAPI (https://pokeapi.co/), which is free and open to use.
All Pokémon names, sprites, and game data are © Nintendo, Game Freak, and The Pokémon Company.

### PokéAPI
- Source: https://pokeapi.co/
- License: Open data, no authentication required
- Attribution: "Pokémon and Pokémon character names are trademarks of Nintendo."

### Pokémon Images & Sprites
All Pokémon images and sprites are copyright of their respective owners:
- © Nintendo
- © Game Freak  
- © The Pokémon Company

These assets are used for educational and reference purposes under fair use.

### Fonts & Icons
- System fonts are used for text rendering
- Pokéball icon is sourced from public domain resources

